Whilst enroute to the capital, Serizawa Kamo, one of the Miburoushigumi
leaders comes across Ibuki Ryunosuke who had been attacked by bandits.

The Roushigumi are a collection of people who share the same ideals, working
towards the goal of become true samurai. As he observes the efforts of Kondo
Isami and Hijikata Toshizo as they work to improve the prestige of the group,
Ryunosuke, who despises samurai, begins to question his way of life.
